# Android

## Apps

* ### Shader Editor
	Create [GLSL](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GLSL) shaders on
	your Android phone and use them as live wallpaper.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in June 2013</span>$(loc ../ShaderEditor app/src/main)</p>

	+ [Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.shadereditor)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/ShaderEditor)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/ShaderEditor/releases)
* ### Binary Eye
	1D and 2D barcode scanner for Android.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in August 2017</span>$(loc ../BinaryEye app/src/main)</p>

	+ [Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.binaryeye)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/BinaryEye)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/BinaryEye/releases)
* ### Libra
	Helps making hard decisions.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in March 2017</span>$(loc ../Libra app/src/main)</p>

	+ [Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.libra)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/Libra)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/Libra/releases)
* ### Moto Score
	Tally counter for motorcyclists to record tours and mistakes.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in February 2014</span>$(loc ../MotoScore app/src/main)</p>

	+ [Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.motoscore)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/MotoScore)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/MotoScore/releases)
* ### Wave Lines Wallpaper
	Live wallpaper showing slowly moving wave lines.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in August 2012</span>$(loc ../WaveLinesWallpaper app/src/main)</p>

	+ [Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.wavelines)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/WaveLinesWallpaper)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/WaveLinesWallpaper/releases)

## Components
* ### CameraView
	A view that shows what the camera sees.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in August 2017</span>$(loc ../CameraView cameraview/src/main)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/CameraView)
* ### ScalingImageView
	ImageView that transforms its drawable according to touch input.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in November 2015</span>$(loc ../ScalingImageView scalingimageview/src/main)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/ScalingImageView)
* ### SwipeImageView
	Swipe/zoom/pinch ImageView.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in January 2017</span>$(loc ../SwipeImageView swipeimageview/src/main)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/SwipeImageView)
* ### Pie Menu
	A zooming pie menu.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in September 2013</span>$(loc ../AndroidPieMenu src)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/AndroidPieMenu)
* ### TouchClock
	Editable clock view.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in September 2013</span>$(loc ../TouchClock src)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/TouchClock)
